platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Beautiful levels and a lovable mustachioed hero take the spotlight in Leos Fortune, a platformer that blends physics-based puzzles and timing challenges with a flurry of fresh concepts and delightfully challenging gameplay. Blast through the air from a pirates cannon, explore underwater caverns, or run for your life during intense chase sequences. Leos Fortune is a feast for the eyes and an immensely satisfying journey from start to finish.
